m_entries.m_key: Hello, I am the test NPC of this developer demo.
m_entries.m_line: Hello, I am the test NPC of this developer demo.

m_entries.m_key: I am here to showcase the features of the dialogue/shop system of this demo!
m_entries.m_line: I am here to showcase the features of the dialogue/shop system of this demo!

m_entries.m_key: What would you like to do?
m_entries.m_line: What would you like to do?

m_entries.m_key: This game is called Reality Bleed.
m_entries.m_line: This game is called Reality Bleed.

m_entries.m_key: It will be a rogue-like bullet hell inspired by HoH, WoW and others.
m_entries.m_line: It will be a rogue-like bullet hell inspired by HoH, WoW and others.

m_entries.m_key: It is currently being developed by a single person!
m_entries.m_line: It is currently being developed by a single person!

m_entries.m_key: My discord is Smc#6127, feel free to contact me!
m_entries.m_line: My discord is Smc#6127, feel free to contact me!

m_entries.m_key: I'll be happy to talk about this all day long! :)
m_entries.m_line: I'll be happy to talk about this all day long! :)

m_entries.m_key: Beautiful day outside! What do you need?
m_entries.m_line: Beautiful day outside! What do you need?

m_entries.m_key: How may I be of service today?
m_entries.m_line: How may I be of service today?

m_entries.m_key: There's a fellow up the road who's been telling me about some issues...
m_entries.m_line: There's a fellow up the road who's been telling me about some issues...

m_entries.m_key: I did need help, but a band of adventurers was faster than you were!
m_entries.m_line: I did need help, but a band of adventurers was faster than you were!

m_entries.m_key: Ah well, that's life isn't it?
m_entries.m_line: Ah well, that's life isn't it?

m_entries.m_key: Someone else already took care of it...
